quote: If you win, you live. If you lose, you die. If you don't fight, you can't win!
Those who cannot sacrifice cannot obtain anything.
It's not about whether you win or lose. It's about whether you fight.
We'll join the Survey Corps. We'll see the outside world with our own eyes.
I'll kill every last one of them. I'll kill every last Titan.
The world outside the walls is cruel. It's filled with suffering.
Humans are weak. We're fragile. But we're also strong. We have the power to change the world.
Freedom is not something you're given. It's something you take.
I'll give everything. I'll give my life to protect my friends.
We'll fight to the very end. We'll never give up.
